critical_positive: The fact that my conversation partner and I had a lot in common and he was able to understand my love for Devil May Cry. As well as us having things in common relating to politics. Plus, my conversation partner was very playful and able to joke around instead of being serious all the time. It was wonderful how we meshed.

begin_memory_text: We got each others interests and introduced ourselves. We figured out we both like video games, such as Devil May Cry and Minecraft. Also, I learnt she's a housewife.

rest_of_day_open: The rest of my week is going to be mainly work related as I've got an essay and a test to study for. I can't really complain, but I've got a chunk of work to do before I can rest up for Halloween and give myself a break from college by going home for a weekend.
critical_positive: My partner and I had similar interests, so it wasn't too hard to figure out what to talk about.
